{"type":null,"faqId":49821,"title":"为何无法唤醒手机/唤醒率很低？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body41254304\"><p class=\"figure\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264039__p27338368\">首先确认下是否打开了语音唤醒功能以及训练的唤醒词是否正确；</p><p class=\"figure\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264039__p44718725\">其次确保唤醒词训练的时候对着MIC，以及保持训练环境安静；</p><p class=\"figure\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264039__p66924213\">正确训练方式：</p><p class=\"figure\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264039__p65447007\">训练的时候最好在相对安静的环境下，建议45&deg;左右握持手机，距离20至40cm，并尽量使用日常生活中最自然的语速、语调进行训练。</p><p class=\"figure\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264039__p52152158\">注意训练唤醒的时候不要距离MIC太近，如果太近的话容易导致破音，导致唤醒率低！</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264039__p66716242\"></p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264039__p63575268\"></p></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022264039","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448615423000,"seriesProductName":"NXT-AL10A,NXT-AL10B,NXT-AL10C,NXT-CL00A,NXT-DL00A,NXT-TL00A","visitedTimes":8,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"不能唤醒手机，不好使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}